pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"70343776239","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"伪勤奋的表现<br>1、做容易的事，重复的事，停留在舒适区<br>2、没有检测学习效果，不关注学习反馈<br>3、只知道唛头苦学，不知道总结学习规律<br>4、道德许可效应导致将准备工作等不相关的行为当作学习本身了","like_count":17},{"had_liked":false,"id":298211,"user_name":"天然","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1097384,"ip_address":"","ucode":"B8B92656BC1FBE","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/be/a8/2a8da07a.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1623960045,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"70343436781","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"跳测律简<br><br>1. 要做跳一跳才能够得着的事<br>2.要及时检测成效<br>3. 要从实践中总结规律<br>4. 要从最简化的形式开始行动","like_count":16},{"had_liked":false,"id":299002,"user_name":"manx00","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1014356,"ip_address":"","ucode":"CA086E73F179E2","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/7a/54/497b1764.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1624422269,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"40279127933","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"个人总结：<br><br>去做踮一踮脚就能够到的事情<br>做事要立刻看到反馈<br>做事之后想要有检测有输出<br>对学习要观察、分析、总结，并调整和完善学习方法<br>把要做的事最简化，直接开始，然后在执行的过程间隙中完善<br><br><br>前一篇是讲如何学习，写一篇是讲如何有效学习","like_count":9},{"had_liked":false,"id":303240,"user_name":"bin","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1049047,"ip_address":"","ucode":"478603A9AB13B4","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/01/d7/f835081c.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1626681897,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"110681","content":"这是爱玩手机","user_name":"作者回复","comment_id":303240,"uid":"2660210","ip_address":"","utype":1,"ctime":1628240691,"user_name_real":"高冷冷"}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"31691452969","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"我老是学习五分钟，抖音三小时，这算不算是道德可行效应","like_count":8,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":2660210,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/28/97