mment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1638066981,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":2,"score":"1638066981","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"常见的“伪勤奋”:<br>1. 总做容易的事情，用来感动自己。<br>2. 总是不停的输入，没有检测，没有输出。<br>3. 总是“傻学”，不总结规律，形成知识体系。<br>4. 将“做计划”等价于“完成做事”，流于表面，不能真正投入做事。<br>我觉得上面第二点和第四点对我影响最大，要时刻切记，不以输出为目的的努力和勤奋，都是耍流氓！","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":321690,"user_name":"Layne","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1479934,"ip_address":"","ucode":"1FEAACD900AB39","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/16/94/fe/5fbf1bdc.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1636994990,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1636994990","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"逃离舒适区，跳出圈子，告别伪勤奋。<br>坚持每天的学习都能有一个总结性的输出。<br>有输出才能真正的学到和掌握知识内容。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":321099,"user_name":"第一装甲集群司令克莱斯特","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1265707,"ip_address":"","ucode":"4E8FBB23AD860B","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/13/50/2b/2344cdaa.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1636679269,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1636679269","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"买了等于会了，收藏夹吃灰，要不得！","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":320876,"user_name":"白泗小林","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1228471,"ip_address":"","ucode":"CEF6A23B70947D","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/12/be/b7/638b5d30.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1636536229,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1636536229","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"道德许可效应:就像我买了很多课，买了就感觉会了，放着吃灰。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":316916,"user_name":"多酱","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1003109,"ip_address":"","ucode":"AC81B4BFC3F354","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/4e/65/1a32dd94.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1634610975,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1634610975","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"1，做踮踮脚能做到的事情；<br>2，检测自己的学习结果，比如可以与人分享、输出笔记；<br>3，学习过程多总结规律；<br>4，少讲形式，直接干，边干边完善。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":314020,"user_name":"三千佛塔烟云下","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":2273366,"ip_address":"","ucode":"79B45A1ABD077D","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/22/b0/56/d3216fe2.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1632805837,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1632805837","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"1.我读过一百多本书，但实际能运用的知识很有限，继续下去即使读了一千本，增强最多的可能只是我的自恋感。因为我没有跳出舒适区，只知道做简单的&quot;输入&quot;，现在，我要到舒适区的边缘，做有一点难度的&quot;输出&quot;，不定太高，每天学的文章都写下评论，再加日更100字的小文章，即可。逃出伪勤奋，并检验学习成果。<br>2.关于反馈，一开始做输出，很可能得不到什么反馈，写的内容没人点赞，没人留言…这时，需要的是坚持，自己创作的内容足够多了，粉丝会日益增加，反馈会像滚雪球一样袭来。<br>3.我也受道德许可效应的支配。每当我晚上健身回来，我总想着去超市买冰棍，这还不够，回到家还要大量地喝饮料。感谢冷冷，让我意识到了这个问题所在。健身使我进步，道德许可效应拉着我退步，我要松开ta的手了。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":311949,"user_name":"Kemal","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1814458,"ip_address":"","ucode":"27FEBE83A4B4DB","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/1b/af/ba/878db4e6.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1631546929,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":1,"score":"1631546929","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"锚定结果，直击本质，追求效率，复盘迭代","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":311642,"user_name":"老马","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1230233,"ip_address":"","ucode":"12D1AA05135F43","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/12/c5/99/78374698.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1631357718,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1631357718","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"线先开枪再瞄准","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":310847,"user_name":"今天你学习了吗？","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1489002,"ip_address":"","ucode":"1CACF4492D7843","user_header":"https://static0